OL,5, A water company has urged customers to 
OL,6, avoid all non-essential water use.     
OL,8,FAffinity Water said "urgent action" was
OL,9,Fneeded in areas of Essex and           
OL,10,FHertfordshire to "conserve reservoir   
OL,11,Fsupplies for everyone".                
OL,13,FThe water supplier said recent water   
OL,14,Fdemand had surged from 209 million     
OL,15,Fgallons (950 million litres) a day to  
OL,16,F242 million gallons (one billion       
OL,17,Flitres) due to the hot weather.        
OL,19,FIt added it was "working around the    
OL,20,Fclock to maintain supplies".           
